name: I MINTED MY FIRST TEZOS NFT with NFTs.tips
description: NFTs.tips is a non profit that helps people learn and onboard into the NFT space. We are teaching people how to mint their first NFT on the Tezos Blockchain. If we helped you with and you wanted to give back, by buying this NFT you will be donating to the NFTs.tips Foundation which is a non profit. For more info go to https://nfts.tips
